  "body": "# LRSS\n<img src='https://badger-api-staging.worldwidepixel.ca/compact?gradientStart=656565&gradientEnd=353535&lineOne=Part%20of&lineTwo=CRSS&colourOne=FFFFFF&colourTwo=FFFFFF&iconUrl=https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/gqGKfy2V/83dee2b1fecd90c6dd80102485bbfdf297f76302.png' alt='Part%20of CRSS' /> <img src='https://badger-api-staging.worldwidepixel.ca/compact?gradientStart=656565&gradientEnd=353535&lineOne=Runs%20in&lineTwo=1.21&colourOne=FFFFFF&colourTwo=FFFFFF&iconUrl=https://github.com/LarsMans64/FancyBlockIcons/blob/main/assets/Icons/axialeaa/crafter.png?raw=true' alt='Runs%20in 1.21' /> <img src='https://badger-api-staging.worldwidepixel.ca/compact?gradientStart=656565&gradientEnd=353535&lineOne=Uses&lineTwo=Fabric&colourOne=FFFFFF&colourTwo=FFFFFF&iconUrl=https://fabricmc.net/assets/logo.png' alt='Uses Fabric' /> <img src='https://badger-api-staging.worldwidepixel.ca/compact?gradientStart=656565&gradientEnd=353535&lineOne=If%20you%20ask%20for%20forge&lineTwo=We%27ll%20steal%20your%20kneecaps&colourOne=FFFFFF&colourTwo=FF0000&iconUrl=https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/778706890914095109/fhMDH9o6_400x400.jpg' alt='If%20you%20ask%20for%20forge We will%20steal%20your%20kneecaps' /> \n\nLRSS was a 1.21 Modded Minecraft server with custom generation, modded structures, biomes, politics and much more.\n\nYou can no longer join LRSS, as it has been shut down. <!-- on the CRSN Lobby with this IP:\n\\`\\`\\`txt\nplay.crss.cc\n\\`\\`\\`\nThere is a button to join the lobby directly on the Modpack. -->\n\n## Rules & Info\n\nYou can find the LRSS rules and info [here](https://git.theclashfruit.me/lrss/lrss) \n\n## Images\n\n![LRSS Banner](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/Cp3Bze59/images/ca429f7fbb0dd8d5f950e3ac732503cb6ed6070f.png) \n\n## Licensing\n\n<p xmlns:cc=\"http://creativecommons.org/ns#\" xmlns:dct=\"http://purl.org/dc/terms/\"><span property=\"dct:title\">LRSS</span> by <a rel=\"cc:attributionURL dct:creator\" property=\"cc:attributionName\" href=\"https://lupancham.net\">Lupancham</a> is marked with <a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/?ref=chooser-v1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"license noopener noreferrer\" style=\"display:inline-block;\">CC0 1.0<img  width=\"16\" height=\"16\" style=\"height:22px!important;margin-left:3px;vertical-align:text-bottom;\" src=\"https://mirrors.creativecommons.org/presskit/icons/cc.svg?ref=chooser-v1\" alt=\"\"><img  width=\"16\" height=\"16\" style=\"height:22px!important;margin-left:3px;vertical-align:text-bottom;\" src=\"https://mirrors.creativecommons.org/presskit/icons/zero.svg?ref=chooser-v1\" alt=\"\"></a></p> \n<p xmlns:cc=\"http://creativecommons.org/ns#\" xmlns:dct=\"http://purl.org/dc/terms/\"><a property=\"dct:title\" rel=\"cc:attributionURL\" href=\"https://crss.cc\">CRSS</a> by <a rel=\"cc:attributionURL dct:creator\" property=\"cc:attributionName\" href=\"https://blurryface.xyz\">Blryface</a> is marked with <a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/?ref=chooser-v1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"license noopener noreferrer\" style=\"display:inline-block;\">CC0 1.0<img   width=\"16\" height=\"16\" style=\"height:22px!important;margin-left:3px;vertical-align:text-bottom;\" src=\"https://mirrors.creativecommons.org/presskit/icons/cc.svg?ref=chooser-v1\" alt=\"\"><img   width=\"16\" height=\"16\" style=\"height:22px!important;margin-left:3px;vertical-align:text-bottom;\" src=\"https://mirrors.creativecommons.org/presskit/icons/zero.svg?ref=chooser-v1\" alt=\"\"></a></p>\n",
